{"tid":1210422,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"唔該有意繼續去野餐嘅女仔著返長褲波鞋","createTime":"2019-06-12T13:44:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-21T01:00:01.000Z","uid":11028,"like":157,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"c920bc462711ac8279825c96d417069631e359d4","tid":1210422,"uid":11028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T13:44:02.000Z","msg":"今日睇到有啲女係著短裙短褲平底鞋<br />\n我唔係想阻你哋嘅衣著自由<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係喺某啲緊急重要時刻<br />\n人地扶你跨過另一邊<br />\n你哋走哂光 我都睇唔少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我自己著長褲波鞋都跨得好狼狽<br />\n你哋要更多時間跨過去 仲有啲係著超厚底嗰種波鞋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁樣其實會令其他人呼吸道/雙眼辛苦多陣<br />\n如果有狗追到黎就冚家產㗎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲有你哋露腿其實無問題<br />\n但喺呢啲情況下 好易刮花你哋啲美腿<br />\n我著長褲都唔知幾時擦損咗腳眼<br />\n<br />\n乖啦 努力埋呢幾日先再著啦好無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申: 絲"},{"pid":"de5181a18dfcb193c4fbc2943af40fb00449899d","tid":1210422,"uid":143945,"like":32,"dislike":0,"score":32,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T14:16:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b45671bc354284b8024ed0956f37f58e26aed4a1","tid":1210422,"uid":11028,"like":37,"dislike":1,"score":36,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T16:56:26.000Z","msg":"今日見到有人share衣著暴露絲打既相<br />\n衷心希望絲打們著返適宜嘅裝束<br />\n我知你哋唔介意俾人睇<br />\n但目前唔係太合適<br />\n啲相見到都唔知對眼放邊好<br />\n應該望你哋搬緊野定重要部位好<br />\n<br />\nPs 國難當前唔好問我拎相<br />\n唔好打攪我阿媽 公海好多人share<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ef86d7885d099b5aa295d65fa203282153c988d","tid":1210422,"uid":11028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T16:56:48.000Z","msg":"Pish <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c500a065f471f2ca30254f55bd65a9f805b137c7","tid":1210422,"uid":33495,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"cit