,"tid":1210422,"uid":207005,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T17:55:50.000Z","msg":"幫手分散黑警注意力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"815884bc902b74097439a763ddf06943c6853802","tid":1210422,"uid":245101,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T18:05:06.000Z","msg":"特別係連登， 比起冇經常上連登既義士，連登班友特別狗公， 做正經野都講廢話"},{"pid":"27986b2cd030205f7152a96642e460010ffbd9dc","tid":1210422,"uid":245101,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T18:05:26.000Z","msg":"但著得舒舒就得"},{"pid":"0135654e018fb8bad9b06bc15ca640523453571f","tid":1210422,"uid":53666,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T18:07:11.000Z","msg":"包實啲 認人都無咁易就真"},{"pid":"820dea816aee3a082a825eb0968226b38d373013","tid":1210422,"uid":11028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T04:02:12.000Z","msg":"Push<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd80632e98c60c7210811df177ae5b452800b8de","tid":1210422,"uid":88123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T04:05:20.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"a278f8d7f5581fb30073a250281b01c66eaa2861","tid":1210422,"uid":210794,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T10:05:32.000Z","msg":"重要post要推<br />\n<br />\n雖然見到咁多絲打著得咁清涼真係好提昇士氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，<br />\n但為安全起見真心唔好著咁少布（例如背心熱褲露腰衫）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n明白妳哋好多和理非冇諗住去前線，但記住啲警犬冇性，一清場真係好危險。咁大表面皮膚外露對住胡椒噴霧、催淚彈都好危險，仲好有可能擦傷，到時又要麻煩醫療人員同浪費醫療物資。為己為人，著返長褲、行動方便嘅衫。<br />\n<br />\n雖然好多巴打都著短褲、唔介意爛腳，但其實都唔係咁好，絲打們更加要小心。<br />\n<br />\n利申6.9到而家發齊咁多個夢，想講呢個問題好耐。"},{"pid":"138865264abffbe8f10d3dc16c58795726c351b0","tid":1210422,"uid":22637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T10:28:06.000Z","msg":"唔該所有出嚟嘅人除曬啲吊住嘅長型耳環/好誇嘅耳環<br />\n走/跑果陣一勾就仆街冚家剷 同埋啲狗影相好易認到你啲&rdquo;特色&rdquo;耳環<br />\n<br />\n有紋身嘅都麻煩遮一遮 又係好易俾狗認到"},{"pid":"6d9b5001430872e73a613f5c8b0bb928d8829b4b","tid":1210422,"uid":119864,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T10:30:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZquRSSQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZquRSSQ.jpg&h=dbab217e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/J6fxCjw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJ6fxCjw.jpg&h=f877fe0e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WXZymMc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWXZymMc.jpg&h=4272234a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7f7f6a2ff46e4546368118d4ddbd51adc8e75da","tid":1210422,"uid":11028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T11:24:54.000Z","msg":"呢種裝束真係好易成為目標<br />\n到時被狗check身份證 交數<br />\n追住打/噴胡椒噴霧etc.<br />\n真係唔好怪人唔提你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外樓上有提到耳環呢樣好啱<br />\n其實最好任何飾物都唔好戴<br />\n呢樣係包括男女<br />\n如果戴咗 到時啲狗討論咬邊個<br />\n飾物係好好嘅特徵黎 紋身更加唔洗講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以一切從簡 樸素 全黑 無飾物<br />\n可以減低被狗捉嘅機會<br />\n如果有必帶嘅野 如玉<br />\n我只可以叫你 盡遮 唔好咁&rsquo;樣&rsquo;眼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c57416814899dea4e44334de95fcf974cdc571ee","tid":1210422,"uid":174013,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T11:29:44.000Z","msg":"依 d場面著低胸背心真係唔知搏乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"590da7eb423361ffccb3e8d4db7c29b4e7619721","tid":1210422,"uid":11028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T07:14:30.000Z","msg":"我無嘢講<br />\n我唔解鎖<br />\n我揾律師<br />\n唔好凶我<br />\n我投訴你<br />\n我要柯屎<br />\n我要食飯<br />\n我要毛氈"},{"pid":"725439acdccfac84946fcc732f2502f4feacaa2a","tid":1210422,"uid":227968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T02:37:02.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">721 和理非都要Full Gear </span></span></strong></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">口號小提議：<br />\n<br />\n1.撤回修例<br />\n2.釋放義士<br />\n3.追究警隊濫權<br />\n4.反西環治港<br />\n5.我要雙普選<br />\n<br />\n有俾人知你真正訴求，<br />\n正經少少唔該</span></span></strong></div>"},{"pid":"27f2fcf5591a45cc21c374ac8ab0a0cfff6f6e36","tid":1210422,"uid":227968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T08:37:59.000Z","msg":"係咪話組隊行街？？<br />\n金鐘？？ <br />\n呢排天氣時好時壞， 出街要帶齊裝備嗰啲唔好曬親又淋雨呀"},{"pid":"1a14dd2d5604b722cd3bd035d1e0c25ada817e07","tid":1210422,"uid":227968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T01:00:01.000Z","msg":"推"}]}